  "texts": [
    "Using a four-fold cross-validation approach, the proposed method was validated on four different datasets with the highest score of Egyptian Arabic to standard Arabic 25.35 bleu score.",
    "This paper 11 recommended a generic method for converting an Egyptian colloquial (Egyptian Dialect) Arabic sentence to a vocalized MSA sentence.",
    "They were using a statistical approach to tokenize and tag Arabic sentences automatically.",
    "As well as a rule-based approach for producing the target diacriticized MSA sentence.",
    "The work was assessed using a dataset of 1 K Egyptian dialect sentences (800 sentences for training and 200 sentences for testing)."
  ],
